<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>
<div class="text-center p-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">About Yelpcamp</h1>
    <p class="lead">This is a Personal Project inspired by Colt Steele's <a href="https://github.com/Colt/YelpCamp"
            target="_blank">Yelpcamp</a></p>
    <hr class="my-4">
</div>
<div class="card container">
    <h1 class="text-center">What is YelpCamp?</h1>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p>
        <span style="color:blueviolet; font-weight: bold;">Yelpcamp</span> is a Campground Reviewing Website. Users can
        create their campgrounds or review others' campgrounds. To get started, simply
        <a href="/register">Register</a>.
    </p>
    <p>This was a project from <a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/the-web-developer-bootcamp/">Web Dev BootCamp
        </a> taught by <strong>Colt Steele</strong>. YelpCamp was created using Node.js, Express and MongoDB.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Create, Edit & Remove Campgrounds</li>
        <li>Informative Cluster Maps to show locations of different campgrounds</li>
        <li>Review Campgrounds posted by others</li>
        <li>Like & Save Campgrounds</li>
        <li>View Information in User Profile about Campgrounds created and liked</li>
    </ul>
</div>
